# Installation

Add this to `~/.config/alacritty/alacritty.yml`

```yaml
colors:
  # Default colors
  primary:
    background: "0x3c4c55"
    foreground: "0xffebc3"

  # Normal colors
  normal:
    black: "0x2d2c29"
    red: "0xff5370"
    green: "0x87af87"
    yellow: "0xf0c38a"
    blue: "0x98b8e6"
    magenta: "0xb888e2"
    cyan: "0x7fc1ca"
    white: "0xd6e9ff"

  # Bright colors
  bright:
    black: "0x918175"
    red: "0xfd8489"
    green: "0xa9dd9d"
    yellow: "0xf0eaaa"
    blue: "0xa8d2eb"
    magenta: "0xe7d5ff"
    cyan: "0xc5d4dd"
    white: "0xffffff"
```
